Class MacroMolecularAction

All Implemented Interfaces:
BatchAction, LoggedAction
Direct Known Subclasses:
MacroMolecularAction
public class MacroMolecularAction
extends MolecularAction
implements BatchAction

Represents a batch of AtomicActions grouped under the same molecule identifier. Typically, this class is used as a container class for calling MEME_BATCH_ACTIONS.macro_action.

Author:
MEME Group
